The voice of the person next to me is so annoying. I wish I could
be moved to the shared room too...

If I were a 'model prisoner'... Well, I touched a prisoner's
butt, so it seems impossible for a while.
Oh, it's so cramped and calming...
\SE[12]There are so many different people here...

The next activity is basketball, right? I'm not really a fan of
it, you know.

Oh, that's right. Well then, how about skipping the exercise and
doing some... adult exercise with me from now on...?
\SE[75]Hey, what are you doing? Hurry up, let's go.

\SE[24] Ah... I was just about to watch Female Knight Lesbian
Battle... \!\SE[58] Laura, please understand my feelings...!

The next activity is basketball, right? I'm not really a fan of
it, you know.

Oh, that's right. If you're skipping the exercise, how about you
and I... engage in some adult exercise...?
\SE[75]Hey, what are you doing? Hurry up, let's go.

\SE[24] Ah... I was just about to watch Female Knight Lesbian
Battle... \!\SE[58] Laura, please understand my feelings...!

Well, you see... I was a teacher at the school and I ended up
devouring one of my students... Then, the parents sued me and
that's why I'm here...

Well, that's in the past now. I hope that incident with the
student I... had my way with... doesn't become a bad memory.

\SE[2]By the time I'm released, I might have become stronger than
you. \SE[3]You might not be able to stand up to me anymore.

No...! That's... great...! To be defeated by my former student in
strength... It's really amazing...
\SE[0]... So you're a writer, huh... Vega.

Ugh... my cellmate got released. They said they'll be waiting for
me...

I can't bear it anymore. What if I end up sexually harassing
another inmate...? Will my sentence be extended and my life
ruined...? Ugh... it's hell...

\SE[33] (Laura has always been waiting for me. \!\SE[58] I will
definitely help her, so...)
Huh? Can't you hear my voice? Haah... I'm lonely...

I... committed indecent acts in the name of God. And that's why I
ended up getting caught... But I have no regrets. How about you?
It's actually quite satisfying.
\SE[59]Please spare me the talk about returning from prison...

I've been watching you fight, and you guys are strong. You give
off a strong couple vibe. By the way... which one of you is the
attacker?
\SE[75] (There are many strong girls in this prison...)

\SE[37]N-No... I-I already have someone I've decided on in my
heart...

I see... \!Big sister...\. I'll be cheering for you. I thought
you and that person over there would make a good match since they
seemed cat-like.

Ugh... Just a little more... It feels like I'm about to see...
Ah, no. The skin on my face is reaching its limit...

When you put your ear against the wall, you can faintly hear a
sweet voice...

\SE[92]... What are you doing? Seriously, your bad taste knows no
bounds.

\SE[2]Your girlfriend's prison is not here. \SE[3]...It's at the
end of the corridor ahead.

Living as a prisoner doesn't seem so bad. We get meals, there are
many colleagues, and we even have relationships with our
cellmates... Could it be that this place is a 'paradise'?
